    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54B32 power plant. This 3.2L atmospheric straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM ceiling. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to address chassis fatigue, and the rod bearings have been serviced for preventative longevity. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows honest road-going patina, the structural integrity and powertrain synchronization are dialed in for spirited driving.",
